  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/1d3052c975fbb1baacedcb90c696cc30.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/93e9cf86f8daca70853d1faff873c25d.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>To complete your missing story, you can be Agriculture, Fishing, Mining, Production, Fighting, Cookery and much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/63733509bb0bc7c89eef46ba7ad94e72.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>Examine Town, Underwater City, Lava Mine, Cloud City and much more areas!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/920ea0ede512a97d18f02c8812c0059d.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>You can befriend or fall in love with the townspeople!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/cee40e61ae45628da14c86ac27bfc775.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>Thanks to the upgradable structures, you can grow your farm more and add richness to your wealth!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/3d1c8cf8c4d4b5c0b3d92d1638fa85af.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>You can fight evil monsters and add strength to your strength with what you get from these monsters and make the town a safe place!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/1d3052c975fbb1baacedcb90c696cc30.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/93e9cf86f8daca70853d1faff873c25d.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>To complete your missing story, you can be Agriculture, Fishing, Mining, Production, Fighting, Cookery and much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/63733509bb0bc7c89eef46ba7ad94e72.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>Examine Town, Underwater City, Lava Mine, Cloud City and much more areas!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/920ea0ede512a97d18f02c8812c0059d.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>You can befriend or fall in love with the townspeople!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/cee40e61ae45628da14c86ac27bfc775.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>Thanks to the upgradable structures, you can grow your farm more and add richness to your wealth!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233950/extras/3d1c8cf8c4d4b5c0b3d92d1638fa85af.avif?t=1681869414\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>You can fight evil monsters and add strength to your strength with what you get from these monsters and make the town a safe place!",
